    "instructions": [
        "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat. Add onion, garlic, carrots, and celery, and sauté for 5–6 minutes until softened.",
        "Stir in oregano, turmeric, pepper, and salt. Pour in vegetable broth and bring to a boil.",
        "Add orzo and cook for 8–10 minutes, stirring occasionally, until al dente.",
        "Stir in chickpeas, lemon juice, and zest. Simmer for 2 minutes.",
        "Add spinach and fresh herbs. Cook just until spinach is wilted. Taste and adjust seasoning before serving hot."
